steps.name: User is on automation page
User verifies that home page is visible successfully
User clicks on 'Signup / Login' button
User verifies 'New User Signup!' is visible
User enters name and email address
User clicks 'Signup' button
User verifies that 'ENTER ACCOUNT INFORMATION' is visible
User fills details: Title, Name, Email, Password, Date of birth
User selects checkbox1 'Sign up for our newsletter!'
User selects checkbox2 'Receive special offers from our partners!'
User fills details: First name, Last name, Company, Address, Address2, Country, State, City, Zipcode, Mobile Number
User clicks 'Create Account button'
